Class BoardFrame

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • java.awt.Window
          • java.awt.Frame
            • javax.swing.JFrame
              • showboard.BoardFrame
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, javax.swing.WindowConstants, IBoard
    public class BoardFrame
extends javax.swing.JFrame
implements IBoard

    The Class BoardFrame.

    This class is just used to load the BoardPanel. It extends JPanel and implements IBoard.

    As the BoardPanel is a private class, BoardPanel is a Facade.

    Version:
    3.0
    Author:
    Anne-Emilie DIET
    See Also:
    JFrame, BoardPanel, Dimension, Rectangle, IBoard, ISquare, IPawn, Serialized Form
